_json.gridTitle: Takeaway Style Wandering Dragon Stir Fry
_json.description: This takeaway style Wandering Dragon is so easy to make at home. In this stir fry the chicken and shrimp are cooked together with plenty of vegetables, a delicious savory brown Chinese sauce, along with garlic and black pepper. This delicious Chinese recipe is healthy and quick to make plus it tastes better than takeout! Serve it with fried rice or noodles for a family dinner that is quick and healthy. Plus I'll show you how to get the soft tender chicken just like your favorite takeaway.
